    "solution": "[Mn(en)<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>] structure is shown below having 6 cis\nN-Mn-Cl bond angles. The dotted markings show the cis\nN-Mn-Cl bond angles.<br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1kwtitw30/da2edcb3-4a18-4a44-8588-6db5e0582f79/1ed94ec0-55f1-11ec-8201-09ef4d4fb1d6/file-1kwtitw31.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1kwtitw30/da2edcb3-4a18-4a44-8588-6db5e0582f79/1ed94ec0-55f1-11ec-8201-09ef4d4fb1d6/file-1kwtitw31.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-height: 50vh\" alt=\"JEE Advanced 2019 Paper 2 Offline Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 49 English Explanation\">",
