    "solution": "<p>Among the given compounds, the compounds of the type [MA$$_2$$X$$_2$$] and [M(AA)$$_2$$X$$_2$$] will exhibit geometrical isomerism.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lfrmrpq0/2566d738-cff7-4633-acc2-00d6200f7885/11bbd780-cd0f-11ed-8124-cf50c8498624/file-1lfrmrpq1.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lfrmrpq0/2566d738-cff7-4633-acc2-00d6200f7885/11bbd780-cd0f-11ed-8124-cf50c8498624/file-1lfrmrpq1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"IIT-JEE 2009 Paper 1 Offline Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 28 English Explanation 1\"><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lfrms182/9ef7441b-b798-4243-a979-3080182bb228/1a9e5120-cd0f-11ed-8124-cf50c8498624/file-1lfrms183.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lfrms182/9ef7441b-b798-4243-a979-3080182bb228/1a9e5120-cd0f-11ed-8124-cf50c8498624/file-1lfrms183.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"IIT-JEE 2009 Paper 1 Offline Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 28 English Explanation 2\"></p>",
